                "comment": "The biggest badass of the British 17th Century...  England's Thomas Paine, only with a better moustache. A snotty, opinionated fiercely educated revolutionary who personally made life about as difficult for the Roundheads as anyone could hope. Imprisoned, unimprisoned, imprisoned again...  Makes Ben Franklin look like a royalist.  The man deserves a decent writeup.",
